node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tyler Cameron in Delnor-Wiggins Pass State Park with @nate_app. May be an image of 1 person, beard and body of water.

node.text: Me staring at you until you preorder my book! Go click the link in my bio, download the @nate_app and follow my summer list to get a free copy of the book! If we make NY Times best sellers list, I'm showing my ass on Instagram!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tyler Cameron on July 21, 2021 tagging @nate_app. May be an image of 2 people.

node.text:
I’ve got an amazing announcement for you all! I’m giving away 10K copies of my new book “You Deserve Better” for FREE! That’s right. I’ve created a list of my summer must haves in partnership with the nate App, and the lucky first 10K to download the app and follow my list will get a free copy shipped to them beginning Aug. 3rd! 

All you have to do:
1. download the nate app
2. follow my list (linked in bio)
3. wait for the gift link in your email inbox (starting August 3rd)

@nate_app #stayinflow #giveaway

node.text: My house is always filled with competition. My brother Ryan is currently the top chef in the house. But he doesn't know that I have recently joined the BBQ Pitmasters - Novice to Expert group on Facebook. It has given me a ton of tips on how to cook on the grill, especially for tomahawk steak. With that group, and a little more practice, I may be the new best chef in the house. #Ad #moretogether @Facebookgroups
